<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><?xml-stylesheet href="http://www.blogger.com/styles/atom.css" type="text/css"?><feed xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom' xmlns:openSearch='http://a9.com/-/spec/opensearchrss/1.0/' xmlns:gd="http://schemas.google.com/g/2005"><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post4814239978597819604..comments</id><updated>2017-05-22T03:33:56.305+08:00</updated><title type='text'>Comments on 编程随想的博客: 跳还是不跳，是一个问题——跳槽时该如何权衡？</title><link rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#feed' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/feeds/comments/default'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default?max-results=999'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html'/><link rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/"/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='//4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><generator version='7.00' uri='http://www.blogger.com'>Blogger</generator><openSearch:totalResults>8</openSearch:totalResults><openSearch:startIndex>1</openSearch:startIndex><openSearch:itemsPerPage>999</openSearch:itemsPerPage><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-365305272061532721</id><published>2017-03-25T10:44:20.076+08:00</published><updated>2017-03-25T10:44:20.076+08:00</updated><title type='text'>很抱歉，博主，虽然文不对题但这里人少，我就在这儿问了：&#xa;1、如何看待维基解密披露的vault7项目？...</title><content type='html'>很抱歉，博主，虽然文不对题但这里人少，我就在这儿问了：&lt;br /&gt;1、如何看待维基解密披露的vault7项目？（刚出厂的苹果设备固件就已经带上了CIA的恶意软件）&lt;br /&gt;2、如果其它设备固件也中了类似“7号仓库”的招，如何尽可能躲避它们的监视？（没有理由认为天朝朝廷不会这么干）&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;3、一个小小的问题，博主在Tor里有IRC频道吗？是否方便透露？</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/365305272061532721'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/365305272061532721'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1490409860076#c365305272061532721' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-528226938"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2017年3月25日 上午10:44:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-7712028973136008581</id><published>2014-02-04T23:41:21.565+08:00</published><updated>2014-02-04T23:41:21.565+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO Alex Wei&#xa;多谢捧场 :)&#xa;&#xa;本文提及的几个评价标准，有的比较容易判断，有的比较难。&#xa;比...</title><content type='html'>TO Alex Wei&lt;br /&gt;多谢捧场 :)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;本文提及的几个评价标准，有的比较容易判断，有的比较难。&lt;br /&gt;比如“公司文化”这项&lt;br /&gt;相对而言是比较容易判断的。&lt;br /&gt;你可以根据该公司对外的宣传、具体的市场运作、等等来判断。甚至在面试的时候留意某些细节，也能“以小见大”看出某些文化。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;比如“个人对公司的影响力”这项&lt;br /&gt;如果你尚未进入这家公司，就比较难判断。即便进入该公司，也需要经历一段时间的了解，才可以作出判断。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/7712028973136008581'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/7712028973136008581'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1391528481565#c7712028973136008581' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/4975686742675487399'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AmZd_cbsMA8/Th5EbQ2_22I/AAAAAAAAAfg/loksvIqGzic/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2014年2月4日 下午11:41:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4975686742675487399</id><published>2014-01-15T14:20:48.553+08:00</published><updated>2014-01-15T14:20:48.553+08:00</updated><title type='text'>恩，现在才看到这个帖子不知道是幸运还是不幸……&#xa;&#xa;我觉得跳槽对于一个我这样的行业新人来说是一件比较棘...</title><content type='html'>恩，现在才看到这个帖子不知道是幸运还是不幸……&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;我觉得跳槽对于一个我这样的行业新人来说是一件比较棘手的事情，很大程度上在于眼光和见识看不了太远。我目前所在的公司是行业内一家“大”公司，但口碑跟产品质量着实堪忧。身处于公司内一个最小的业务单元中，你可以把事情做得很精致，但很难说对整个产业有清楚的认识。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;我从毕业到现在3年，不敢说做得很不错，但自认为也是兢兢业业，努力学习。但即使如此，当我去面试新的公司的时候才发现有太多看不明白，无法了解的机会或是陷阱在前面。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;很赞成你说的几点评价标准，但即便如此，我也没办法对将要去的新公司有一个更客观的评价。因为我虽然知道这些东西存在，却没有一个有效的评估手段。如果可以，希望能为我们这些职场菜鸟们做一些更加细致的介绍，谢谢。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/4975686742675487399'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/4975686742675487399'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1389766848553#c4975686742675487399' title=''/><author><name>Alex Wei</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/08184501222386019221</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='32' height='32' src='//lh5.googleusercontent.com/-qpE3NI2tAEA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAA4/3McaE_arUiA/s512-c/photo.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-2042221415"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2014年1月15日 下午2:20:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2415057882497006538</id><published>2013-05-28T21:32:28.859+08:00</published><updated>2013-05-28T21:32:28.859+08:00</updated><title type='text'>其实在招聘过程中，双方互相都缺乏了解，获取的信息都比较有限。&#xa;除非是有朋友推荐，或许会好一些。&#xa;&#xa;对...</title><content type='html'>其实在招聘过程中，双方互相都缺乏了解，获取的信息都比较有限。&lt;br /&gt;除非是有朋友推荐，或许会好一些。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;对于求职者而言，可以利用面试过程，通过仔细观察、通过对面试官提问，来获取信息。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;另外，你提到的“生存环境不断下滑”&lt;br /&gt;如今貌似所有行业都面临这个问题。&lt;br /&gt;天朝的大环境比较糟糕——高房价、高通胀......</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/2415057882497006538'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/2415057882497006538'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1369747948859#c2415057882497006538' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/3920295417158545550'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AmZd_cbsMA8/Th5EbQ2_22I/AAAAAAAAAfg/loksvIqGzic/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2013年5月28日 下午9:32:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3920295417158545550</id><published>2013-05-26T09:17:25.722+08:00</published><updated>2013-05-26T09:17:25.722+08:00</updated><title type='text'> 初看 这篇博客，对我们影响很大，帮助颇多。而在求职当中，求职者获取公司的信息往往不对称。&#xa;写道这里...</title><content type='html'> 初看 这篇博客，对我们影响很大，帮助颇多。而在求职当中，求职者获取公司的信息往往不对称。&lt;br /&gt;写道这里又延伸到：&lt;br /&gt;   1.软件公司在不同地区偏差还是比较大的，北上广居多。&lt;br /&gt;   2.外在的、内在的生存环境不断下滑，现在年轻人”逃离“北上广，这种心理似乎很普遍。&lt;br /&gt;   3.软件行业位于十大 “高危猝死”行业。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/3920295417158545550'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/3920295417158545550'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1369531045722#c3920295417158545550' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-436966058"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2013年5月26日 上午9:17:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8529312973021074918</id><published>2009-11-13T11:45:21.816+08:00</published><updated>2009-11-13T11:45:21.816+08:00</updated><title type='text'>我也是在考虑，都一年了，还在考虑。&#xa;to be or not to be....&#xa;明年春天再说。</title><content type='html'>我也是在考虑，都一年了，还在考虑。&lt;br /&gt;to be or not to be....&lt;br /&gt;明年春天再说。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/8529312973021074918'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/8529312973021074918'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1258083921816#c8529312973021074918' title=''/><author><name>fancylea</name><uri>http://blog.csdn.net/fancylea</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1873990149"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年11月13日 上午11:45:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-637752894022604648</id><published>2009-11-12T22:18:35.419+08:00</published><updated>2009-11-12T22:18:35.419+08:00</updated><title type='text'>楼上的同学：&#xa;你可以和你的老板沟通一下，看看是否可以在后续半年的集成工作时，再同时承担另外一些工作。...</title><content type='html'>楼上的同学：&lt;br /&gt;你可以和你的老板沟通一下，看看是否可以在后续半年的集成工作时，再同时承担另外一些工作。&lt;br /&gt;沟通时注意一下沟通技巧，让老板明白你是愿意做事的人。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/637752894022604648'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/637752894022604648'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1258035515419#c637752894022604648' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_itipB8vBZzQ/SY1isusKAfI/AAAAAAAAAGo/4YF360m0Yto/S220/Thinker_BlogSpot.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年11月12日 下午10:18:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3583544261867871773</id><published>2009-11-12T16:09:27.423+08:00</published><updated>2009-11-12T16:09:27.423+08:00</updated><title type='text'>最近我也正在考虑跳槽的问题，因为本人负责的产品将要部署在生产环境了，开发工作接近尾声，基本没什么事了...</title><content type='html'>最近我也正在考虑跳槽的问题，因为本人负责的产品将要部署在生产环境了，开发工作接近尾声，基本没什么事了，但后续集成工作很可能还要持续半年时间。在公司也呆了快18个月了，总觉得该换个环境了，但多少心里有点放不下，毕竟说走就走，手头挑子一撂，给人感觉太不负责任。&lt;br /&gt;博主觉得我应该怎么平衡这里面的关系呢，公司老板同事都对我不错（就是薪水少了点），不想毁了自己形象。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/3583544261867871773'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4814239978597819604/comments/default/3583544261867871773'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html?showComment=1258013367423#c3583544261867871773' title=''/><author><name>Jeff</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/17822553566943390340</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/b16-rounded.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/11/job-hopping.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4814239978597819604' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4814239978597819604' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-720811528"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年11月12日 下午4:09:00"/></entry></feed>